<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/school-hero.png');">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Hostel Facilities</h1>
                    <p>A safe, comfortable, and nurturing home away from home for our students.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div style="flex: 2; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2>A Nurturing Environment for Growth and Learning</h2>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">N.R.K. Public School offers well-maintained and secure
                                hostel facilities for both boys and girls, providing a supportive environment conducive
                                to academic success and personal development. Our hostel aims to be a home away from
                                home, where students learn to live independently, cultivate friendships, and grow into
                                responsible individuals under careful supervision.</p>

                            <div
                                style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                                <div class="card"
                                    style="padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); background: white;">
                                    <h3
                                        style="color: var(--primary-blue); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                        Comfortable Amenities</h3>
                                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-bed text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Spacious Rooms:</strong> Well-ventilated and furnished rooms
                                                with comfortable beds and study areas.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-utensils text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Nutritious Meals:</strong> A balanced and hygienic diet served
                                                in the dining hall, catering to student nutritional needs.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-book-reader text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Supervised Study Hours:</strong> Dedicated time for supervised
                                                study to ensure academic progress.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-table-tennis text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Recreation:</strong> Common rooms with indoor games and outdoor
                                                play areas for relaxation.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-user-md text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Medical Care:</strong> First-aid facilities with a visiting
                                                doctor for routine health check-ups.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-tshirt text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Laundry Services:</strong> Regular laundry services for
                                                students.</div>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>

                                <div class="card"
                                    style="padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); background: white;">
                                    <h3
                                        style="color: var(--primary-blue); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                        Safety and Supervision</h3>
                                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-shield-alt text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>24/7 Security:</strong> Round-the-clock security personnel and
                                                CCTV surveillance to ensure student safety.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-user-tie text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Experienced Wardens:</strong> Dedicated and caring wardens who
                                                oversee the well-being and discipline of students.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-id-card text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Strict Entry/Exit Protocols:</strong> Controlled access to the
                                                hostel premises.</div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start;"><i
                                                class="fas fa-ambulance text-gold"
                                                style="margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                                            <div><strong>Emergency Preparedness:</strong> Clear emergency procedures and
                                                drills in place.</div>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <h3>Typical Daily Routine</h3>
                            <p>A structured daily routine helps students maintain discipline, focus on their studies,
                                and develop healthy habits.</p>
                            <div style="background: var(--bg-cream); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                                <ul style="margin: 0;">
                                    <li><strong>Morning:</strong> Wake-up, freshen up, exercise/yoga, breakfast.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Daytime:</strong> School classes, lunch.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Evening:</strong> Supervised study hours, recreation time, dinner.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Night:</strong> Preparation for the next day, lights out.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                        </div>

                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div
                                style="background: var(--primary-blue); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px;">
                                <h3 style="color: var(--accent-gold);">Hostel Admission</h3>
                                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Hostel seats are limited and allotted on a first-come,
                                    first-served basis. Priority is given to outstation students.</p>
                                <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">To apply for a hostel seat, please tick the 'Hostel
                                    Required' option in the admission form.</p>
                                <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button secondary"
                                    style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Inquire About Availability</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>